title: Liquidity in CLOS Much Better Than People Think: Kerschner
description:
Investors are increasingly weary of restrictions in private credit funds. John Kerschner, Global Head of Securitized Products & Portfolio Manager at Janus Henderson joins "ETF IQ" to discuss. 

 (Source: Bloomberg)
